# Local dev only (optional). Points fetch() at your local Nest backend.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
#
# Production (S3 + CloudFront): leave unset. The app calls https://<your-distribution>/api
# (CloudFront behavior /api/* → ALB). Never bake in http://*.elb.amazonaws.com — mixed content.
